{{!--
/**
 * Spell List Manager Main Layout Template
 *
 * PURPOSE:
 * Primary structural template for the spell list manager application providing
 * the overall container and state management for loading and error conditions.
 * Serves as the foundation for the three-panel spell list management interface
 * while handling application-level states and shared component integration.
 *
 * CONTEXT REQUIREMENTS:
 * @param {boolean} isLoading - Whether application is in loading state
 * @param {boolean} hasError - Whether application has encountered an error
 * @param {string} errorMessage - Error message text for display (when hasError is true)
 *
 * HELPER DEPENDENCIES:
 * @requires localize - Foundry VTT localization helper for text translation
 * @requires if - Handlebars conditional helper for state checks
 * @requires > - Handlebars partial inclusion helper for shared components
 *
 * ACCESSIBILITY FEATURES:
 * - Application role container for screen reader application identification
 * - Loading and error states use shared accessible components
 * - Container classes provide styling context for different application states
 * - Semantic structure supports overall application layout
 *
 * CUSTOMIZATION POINTS:
 * - Container styling adapts to loading and error states through CSS classes
 * - Loading spinner size and message configurable through component parameters
 * - Error display uses shared component for consistency across application
 * - Application state management through conditional rendering
 *
 * INTEGRATION:
 * - Connects to SpellListManager application as primary container
 * - Uses shared components for loading and error state display
 * - Serves as foundation for three-panel manager interface layout
 * - Supports application-level state management and error handling
 * - Works with part-based rendering system for panel management
 */
--}}

<div class="gm-spell-list-manager-container {{#if isLoading}}loading-state{{else if hasError}}error-state{{/if}}"
	role="application">

	{{#if isLoading}}
		<!-- Application Loading State -->
		{{> "modules/spell-book/templates/components/loading-spinner.hbs" size=3 message=(localize "SPELLMANAGER.Application.Loading")}}
	{{else if hasError}}
		<!-- Application Error State -->
		{{> "modules/spell-book/templates/components/error-message.hbs" message=errorMessage}}
	{{/if}}
</div>
